## 模塊 4: VBA 基礎

### 4.1 錄製宏並修改
```vba
Sub 格式化報表()
    ' 選擇全部數據
    Range("A1").CurrentRegion.Select
    
    ' 自動調整欄寬
    Selection.Columns.AutoFit
    
    ' 置中對齊
    Selection.HorizontalAlignment = xlCenter
    
    ' 添加邊框
    Selection.Borders.LineStyle = xlContinuous
End Sub
```

### 4.2 循環處理
```vba
Sub 處理多個工作表()
    Dim ws As Worksheet
    For Each ws In ThisWorkbook.Worksheets
        ' 對每個工作表執行操作
        ws.Range("A1").Value = "已處理"
    Next ws
End Sub
```

