## 模塊 5: Python + Excel

### 5.1 Pandas 讀寫 Excel
```python
import pandas as pd

# 讀取 Excel
df = pd.read_excel('stock_list.xlsx', sheet_name='Sheet1')

# 數據處理
filtered = df[(df['Shape'] == 'RBC') & (df['Carat'] > 5)]

# 保存到新文件
filtered.to_excel('filtered_stock.xlsx', index=False)
```

